  "text": "Generation and purification of virus-like particles (VLPs) were performed as described elsewhere [CITATION_1] . In brief, ZEBOV VLP VP40-GP and VLP VP40 were generated by transient transfection of HEK 293T cells with plasmids encoding ZEBOV VP40 and/or ZEBOV GP 1,2 [CITATION_2] and quantitated by electronmicroscopic particle counting [CITATION_3] and a DC protein assay (BioRad, Mississauga, Ontario).",
